To create a new issue, create a file called issue<num>.html, where <num> is the issue number.

Please, before announcing a new issue, check to see that the page is valid.

To add icons:

Check the icons into images/icons and images/newsletter

example with a subtitle

  <div class="postheader">Focus on Package(s)</div>
  <img class="face" src="/images/newsletter/package-new.png" width="85" height="85" alt="" /><br />

To call fancybox for your thumbnails:

add id="imagebox" in <a href="">

example

<a id="imagebox" href="http://frugalware.org/images/newsletter/issue75_screenshot_juffed.png"><img src="http://frugalware.org/images/newsletter/issue75_screenshot_juffed_t.png" alt="Screenshot of Juffed text editor"></a>
